Package net.sf.mmm.client.base.gwt.dialog Description

Contains the base implementation of the Client Dialog API using GWT.

Client Dialog Base (GWT)

This package and its sub-package contains the base implementation of the Client Dialog API using GWT (Google Web Toolkit), GWTP (GWT-Platform) and GIN (GWT INjection).
In addition this contains MVP base classes extending GWTP to provide a complete client framework.
